oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Interview and performance - Del McCoury - 2016-09-22
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interview with and performance by Del McCoury and band from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on September 22, 2016. Presented in partnership with the Americana Music Association.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Del McCoury;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Interview conducted by Jay Orr. Includes audio from video. Discussion of current album Del and Woody. Comments by Woody Guthrie center executive director Deana McCloud. Performances include: The New York Trains -- Cheap Mike -- Ain't A Gonna Do -- Left In This World Alone -- Californy Gold -- Because You Took Me In Out Of The Rain -- The Government Road -- Dirty Overhalls -- Family Reunion.
